1
00:00:40,399 --> 00:00:41,679
You care that much about Bai Zimei?

2
00:00:42,520 --> 00:00:44,039
Then where the Key of Fate is kept

3
00:00:44,600 --> 00:00:45,640
must have something to do with her

4
00:00:47,079 --> 00:00:48,119
But Bai Zimei's things...

5
00:00:48,119 --> 00:00:49,479
I don't think I've ever seen them

6
00:00:51,439 --> 00:00:53,600
Why would Sheng Shizhong keep something like this?

7
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:10,959
Is this Sheng Shizhong and Bai Zimei?

8
00:01:13,640 --> 00:01:15,439
But this villa is...

9
00:01:32,359 --> 00:01:33,040
Found it

10
00:01:39,719 --> 00:01:40,239
This is it

11
00:01:40,719 --> 00:01:42,079
This is the place in the photo

12
00:01:42,680 --> 00:01:44,120
So Sheng Shizhong and Bai Zimei

13
00:01:44,280 --> 00:01:45,200
used to live here

14
00:01:45,799 --> 00:01:47,280
I never heard Nanny Shen mention it

15
00:01:59,159 --> 00:02:01,120
Empty for so long, yet it's still so clean

16
00:02:01,959 --> 00:02:03,560
Looks like Sheng Shizhong really cared about this place

17
00:02:18,080 --> 00:02:18,800
This is...

18
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:20,319
Bai Zimei

19
00:02:24,800 --> 00:02:26,280
So this really is connected to her

20
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:37,800
The time on this watch is wrong

21
00:02:59,719 --> 00:03:01,719
So it really is the Key of Fate

22
00:03:07,639 --> 00:03:09,400
As long as I eat with Sheng Shizhong's spoon

23
00:03:10,199 --> 00:03:11,560
I'll have his memories from the past

24
00:03:12,759 --> 00:03:13,639
Sheng Shizhong

25
00:03:14,599 --> 00:03:16,840
Let's see what you really went through

26
00:03:24,159 --> 00:03:24,599
This is...

27
00:03:25,319 --> 00:03:26,719
Sheng Shizhong when he was young

28
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:36,919
The new driver, Hu Jin

29
00:03:37,199 --> 00:03:38,759
Just call me Xiao Hu. Hello, Madam

30
00:03:41,080 --> 00:03:42,159
Sheng Shizhong

31
00:03:45,159 --> 00:03:46,599
This is Sheng Shizhong's memory

32
00:03:47,759 --> 00:03:48,439
Slow down, Madam

33
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:08,520
People, you know...

34
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:10,599
how can the gap be so wide?

35
00:04:11,840 --> 00:04:14,159
Born on the exact same day

36
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:16,600
yet he has everything

37
00:04:18,959 --> 00:04:20,000
Money

38
00:04:21,319 --> 00:04:22,160
A wife

39
00:04:23,079 --> 00:04:24,560
and an obedient son

40
00:04:28,079 --> 00:04:28,480
Yeah

41
00:04:29,639 --> 00:04:30,959
Because he has money

42
00:04:31,839 --> 00:04:34,040
that's why he has everything

43
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:35,319
Envy

44
00:04:36,360 --> 00:04:37,040
Jealousy

45
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:38,639
Hatred

46
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:42,079
Never thought you'd feel that way too

47
00:04:52,639 --> 00:04:55,560
Why doesn't a life like this belong to me?

48
00:05:22,560 --> 00:05:24,519
You can't even figure out something so simple

49
00:05:25,319 --> 00:05:27,240
How does someone like that deserve to be Boss?

50
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:32,199
Hello, Boss

51
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:34,199
I saw your desk was messy

52
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:35,680
so I tidied it up for you

53
00:05:37,240 --> 00:05:37,680
It's fine

54
00:05:38,399 --> 00:05:40,160
If you're interested in the books in my study,

55
00:05:40,160 --> 00:05:41,000
feel free to read them anytime

56
00:06:03,879 --> 00:06:04,800
Young man

57
00:06:05,720 --> 00:06:06,519
I'm hungry

58
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:09,600
Can I have one of your roasted sweet potatoes?

59
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:11,639
I won't take it for free

60
00:06:12,160 --> 00:06:13,759
I'll trade you something precious

61
00:06:16,079 --> 00:06:16,680
Something precious?

62
00:06:17,879 --> 00:06:19,399
The Key of Fate

63
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:24,360
A magic spoon that can swap fates

64
00:07:07,519 --> 00:07:08,360
Get the hell out

65
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:09,959
You're not my husband

66
00:07:09,959 --> 00:07:10,959
You are the devil

67
00:07:11,279 --> 00:07:12,680
Give me back Sheng Shizhong

68
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:14,079
Give him back!

69
00:07:16,199 --> 00:07:17,120
Give it up

70
00:07:18,399 --> 00:07:20,680
Unless you switch him back for me

71
00:07:21,319 --> 00:07:24,160
or I'll expose your secret to everyone

72
00:07:24,759 --> 00:07:26,240
No one will believe

73
00:07:26,759 --> 00:07:28,680
a crazy woman's words

74
00:07:36,680 --> 00:07:37,079
Someone!

75
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:41,519
Don't you stop me!

76
00:07:41,519 --> 00:07:41,959
Madam

77
00:07:42,199 --> 00:07:43,160
Don't listen to him!

78
00:07:43,959 --> 00:07:44,759
He's not Sheng Shizhong

79
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:45,920
He's Hu Jin

80
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:47,439
Don't let Madam leave the house

81
00:07:48,160 --> 00:07:49,319
Hurry and call Dr. Lin over

82
00:07:55,839 --> 00:07:56,319
Chairman Sheng

83
00:07:57,480 --> 00:07:58,920
She's already been given a sedative

84
00:07:59,399 --> 00:08:00,920
She should sleep until tomorrow morning

85
00:08:02,199 --> 00:08:02,680
Thanks

86
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:05,199
Sorry to drag you here so late

87
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:07,079
It's nothing. It's my job

88
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:10,560
Oh, right

89
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:14,519
Who is this Hu Jin Madam keeps talking about?

90
00:08:18,759 --> 00:08:19,680
It's embarrassing to say

91
00:08:20,639 --> 00:08:21,319
Hu Jin

92
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:23,199
was the driver I hired for Madam

93
00:08:24,079 --> 00:08:24,800
I never expected the two of them

94
00:08:24,800 --> 00:08:25,920
to end up having an affair

95
00:08:28,519 --> 00:08:29,319
I understand

96
00:08:30,279 --> 00:08:32,399
No wonder when I spoke with Madam before,

97
00:08:33,080 --> 00:08:34,240
even though she rambled on,

98
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:35,360
saying you weren't Sheng Shizhong

99
00:08:35,759 --> 00:08:36,559
but Hu Jin

100
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:39,720
her speech was clear

101
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:40,600
and her thinking was coherent

102
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:43,240
She didn't seem mentally ill at all

103
00:08:43,720 --> 00:08:46,320
Looks like we need further evaluation

104
00:08:46,639 --> 00:08:48,919
Long-term sedative injections

105
00:08:49,360 --> 00:08:51,039
aren't the best treatment

106
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:53,840
Got it

107
00:08:56,399 --> 00:08:57,039
Dr. Lin

108
00:08:57,799 --> 00:08:59,000
About my wife's condition...

109
00:08:59,919 --> 00:09:00,639
I hope

110
00:09:01,799 --> 00:09:03,159
you'll keep it strictly confidential

111
00:09:03,559 --> 00:09:04,120
After all,

112
00:09:05,320 --> 00:09:07,120
I don't want the Sheng family's business

113
00:09:07,519 --> 00:09:09,600
to become idle gossip

114
00:09:10,480 --> 00:09:11,639
Of course

115
00:09:12,279 --> 00:09:14,879
By the way, you're such a skilled doctor

116
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:17,399
Have you ever thought about going independent

117
00:09:17,399 --> 00:09:18,200
and opening your own hospital?

118
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:21,559
A hospital?

119
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:24,879
That would take far too much money

120
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:26,240
I wouldn't dare dream of it

121
00:09:27,279 --> 00:09:29,679
I'm actually very interested in healthcare

122
00:09:30,720 --> 00:09:32,200
Let's talk sometime

123
00:09:35,200 --> 00:09:36,600
Then thank you so much, Mr. Sheng

124
00:09:38,600 --> 00:09:39,279
It's nothing

125
00:09:40,480 --> 00:09:41,200
I'll let you get back to it

126
00:09:41,799 --> 00:09:42,600
I'll head back first

127
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:54,559
Mom

128
00:09:55,039 --> 00:09:55,879
I want Mom

129
00:09:55,879 --> 00:09:56,159
Come here

130
00:09:57,440 --> 00:09:58,399
I'm sorry, Yuanzhou

131
00:09:59,159 --> 00:10:00,200
Mom won't be around

132
00:10:01,879 --> 00:10:03,480
to see you grow up

133
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:05,519
But promise me

134
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:08,480
you'll grow up safe and sound

135
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:11,519
then find your real father

136
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:12,360
Shut up

137
00:10:12,919 --> 00:10:14,120
You crazy woman

138
00:10:16,759 --> 00:10:17,240
Son

139
00:10:18,039 --> 00:10:19,639
Your mother betrayed me

140
00:10:20,519 --> 00:10:22,120
so she can't keep

141
00:10:22,120 --> 00:10:23,919
living in this world

142
00:10:24,480 --> 00:10:25,600
Anyone who won't obey Father

143
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:28,519
must disappear forever

144
00:10:29,039 --> 00:10:29,559
So

145
00:10:30,600 --> 00:10:32,919
you must never defy Father's orders

146
00:10:36,360 --> 00:10:37,080
Understand?

147
00:10:41,519 --> 00:10:42,559
For your son's sake,

148
00:10:43,039 --> 00:10:44,120
it's time for you to go

149
00:10:44,600 --> 00:10:45,159
Let me go!

150
00:10:45,159 --> 00:10:45,799
Yuanzhou

151
00:10:46,399 --> 00:10:46,799
Close your eyes

152
00:10:46,919 --> 00:10:47,480
Don't you dare!

153
00:10:48,120 --> 00:10:49,039
I want your son

154
00:10:49,039 --> 00:10:50,559
to watch you die with his own eyes

155
00:10:51,320 --> 00:10:53,000
Then he'll remember forever

156
00:10:53,480 --> 00:10:55,879
what happens to anyone who defies me

157
00:10:55,879 --> 00:10:56,799
Let me go!

158
00:10:56,799 --> 00:10:57,519
Yuanzhou

159
00:10:58,200 --> 00:10:59,799
You have to live on

160
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:01,919
Be brave

161
00:11:02,519 --> 00:11:04,919
Put on those red high heels

162
00:11:05,240 --> 00:11:07,519
I picked them out just for you

163
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:17,120
Mom!

164
00:11:18,360 --> 00:11:19,120
Yuanzhou!

165
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:20,120
Mom!

166
00:11:27,679 --> 00:11:28,639
No!

167
00:11:48,759 --> 00:11:50,879
Sheng Shizhong, you Beast!
